Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你振作点啊,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵的情况很危急
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,把眼睛张开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你会回不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟幻人那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是放着不管,梵会…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵会被带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…应该不是天堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵…回去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你振作点啊,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经过了三米特了\N（约地球时间一分半钟）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少得快帮小瞳急救才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要想办法,把梵大人给带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有听到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,拜托您回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是国王,了不起,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多亏你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基米尔、达雷特、歇士达、迦迪、比欧雷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在这种小战役就送掉性命\N这样只能被当成是笑话一则嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别扔下我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别扔下我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别扔下我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻弗雷特公国,使我们成功得到能源点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在挂念龙是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙的命运被雾所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模糊不清
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给我处理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经着手进行下一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把龙给我抓来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我的手握剑会颤抖?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着为他担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但从那之后,他就一直都是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是凡身为剑客,都必须克服的考验
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾经历过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自满与傲慢让自己陷入恐惧之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近来常找剑客比试的小子,就是你,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没胆跟我打的话,就把钱全都交出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我就饶你不死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你对自己蛮有信心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报上名来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连·歇萨尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一较高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素质不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却仅执着于技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你的剑中看不到光明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必那么想寻死?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:11:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于没有家与家人的我,剑就是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然输了我哪还能厚着脸皮继续活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使剑惫的不是力量也不是技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其真意就在自己本身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好锻炼你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我与师父巴尔卡斯的相识经过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父他让当时堕落至极的我,见识了何谓光明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑是用来磨练自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但至今我仍无法接近师父的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既了不起又坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人又很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…对剑不是很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想那家伙一定不会把我的话听进去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是你说的话,他就一定听得进去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你人又好又受大家景仰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候你倒挺像恶魔的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从幻之月来的小瞳身带奇妙的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流着龙神人之血的梵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上想要能源点的寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件接着一件发生的奇妙事件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里头一定有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…德莱甸,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢我什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客套话就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟道谢是不用花钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是觉得自己看错你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才打算来为至今的失礼致歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做事当然都是有目的的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能让你卸下心防我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是想要的东西就一定会去夺取
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当是以物易物好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是家父留在书房中\N他最后的航海日志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西对你有用吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有用,有用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能就此解开你们身边的所有谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谜团?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:14:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常听我老爸说你父亲一直在找寻亚特兰提斯的秘宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我就先借走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还真是有名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连在这种边境都能让我颜面无光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和德莱甸代垫的艾斯嘉科尼修理费相比
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来得便宜多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对,确实没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干嘛那么多话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这简直就跟花痴没两样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想为我朋友的事问问你的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位朋友有位交往中的男友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那个人其实是个花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且竟然还有私生子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差劲透了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先听我说完
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却有另一个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是个有钱又温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上我那个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都那么明显了还听不懂,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她应该怎么办才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我发现对方隐瞒自己\N有孩子的事实跟我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我就不会再理他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那种男人实在太没用了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他根本就是来者不拒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…他人很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个不是也很好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表是及格了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有爱情跟经济能力对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就决定是他了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太算计了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要不要先脚踏两条船试试?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不检点了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要不要两边都放弃算了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲剧女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:16:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那…不关我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我那个朋友长久以来的心意怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果问题还是出在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是照自己的心意去做最为自然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来算算看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看哪个人比较适合你那个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这方面倒是挺准的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你个头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在帮人算之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你先搞清楚自己的心意行不行?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是喜欢梵大人还是亚连啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对梵的感情只是担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心…真的只是那样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就别再接近梵大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不适合亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊,是那个对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会在这种地方遇上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就证明了我们有多幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去跟弗肯大人的伴手礼,打声招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个主意好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果就被我家的婆娘抓包了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫艾斯嘉科尼的人型装甲就在这里,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把它交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不照办的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把你们全宰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈的…寨巴哈的人型装甲出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵\N梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去,你还没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵去应战了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一□气把它解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹部有机可乘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度竟然解决不了这种货色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪弗肯大人会对他感到失望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该来做个了结了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢做坏事,你们逃不掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们休想…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们休想杀死梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没那个心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,居然目出一只猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就先打到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好您平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人\N梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了,我全都懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不出我所料一切的答案都在幻之谷里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是传说中龙神人的居住地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歇士达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之月?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受引导之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:57.56,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:06.01,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:13.64,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:19.79,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:22.15,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.39,0:22:27.16,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃烧般的神秘双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:31.00,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真无邪的笑容让我倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:34.80,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深处的暗示只传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:38.81,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了无止尽的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:42.31,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心的鼓动无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.37,0:22:49.78,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想带着你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:57.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:06.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:13.64,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:19.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:22.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.39,0:22:27.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:30.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:34.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:38.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:42.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.37,0:22:49.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい


